I"õ<h3 id="lightweight">Lightweight</h3>

<p>Figmac is only 1.5MB, making it x88 times smaller than the official Figma desktop app.</p>

<h3 id="touch-bar">Touch Bar</h3>

<p>Figmac supports your Macs Touch Bar delivering a more productive workflow.</p>

<h3 id="native-tabs">Native Tabs</h3>

<p>Figmac supports native MacOS window tabs for a more natural Mac experience.</p>

<h3 id="figma-files">Figma Files</h3>

<p>Figmac recognizes .fig files and automatically imports them when they are clicked in Finder.</p>

<h3 id="keyboard-shortcuts">Keyboard Shortcuts</h3>

<p>Figmac supports all of your favourite Figma keyboard shortcuts.</p>

<h3 id="secure">Secure</h3>

<p>Figmac is sandboxed and notarized by Apple for added security and peace of mind.</p>
